               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410614-name-387" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-387" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-387" type="surname" value="GARDINER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-387" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN GARDINER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am journeyman to William Trew. I was out with his bread on the 18th of May—there was one 4lb. loaf in my basket a Devonshire-place, the prisoner came, stole a loaf out of my basket, and ran away with it—I did not know him before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410614-name-388" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-388" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
